com.nftworlds.wallet.contracts.wrappers.common.ERC721Metadata
public class ERC721Metadata extends org.web3j.tx.Contract
Standard contract wrapper for ERC721 contract interactions on any chain. Provides access to ERC721 metadata metadata related functionality that the ERC721 wrapper does not have. Auto-generated with web3j version 4.1.1
